1.0.1 2020-01-12
  - Add pilot scan protocol PDF.
1.0.0 Pilot data acquisition
- Initial acquisition of pilot data for testing of complex-valued, multi-echo EPI data.
README:
DIVA is a new study in which we will acquire a large amount of neuroimaging, neuropsychological, demographic, and physiological data for a small sample of ~3 participants.

Notes
-----
sub-PILOT_ses-01_task-localizerDetection_run-01, sub-PILOT_ses-01_task-localizerDetection_run-01, and sub-PILOT_ses-01_task-StrangerThingsS01E01_run-01 were run without audio.

Please contact Taylor Salo if you observe any irregularities in the dataset.

Taylor Salo
tsalo006@fiu.edu
